==English==
=== Noun ===
'''lemming'''
# a small [[Arctic]] [[rodent]], similar in appearance to the [[hamster]], that resides in the [[tundra]] regions of North America and Europe. Every year at migration time, they flock to the edge of a cliff, and all jump of in mass suicide. A very small number survive, only enough to keep the species alive.

